{"title":"长虹架在彩云中","authors":["胡志良"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":10,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长虹架在彩云中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四处　胡志良"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶蓝天胆气豪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月星辰肩上挑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥工立下愚公志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"移山倒海修大桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电焊女工驾彩云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧剪钢铁架长虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银光闪闪金花落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长虹架在彩云中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严冬飞雪冰封道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江面寒风如虎啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铆工迈步上桥梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手持枪向天笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥梁工人是英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手持彩笔画长虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛万顷脚下踩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗忠心向阳红。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}